(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 220.98 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c09d6bc0-086f-4ef0-b9ee-f17187a78914))
(text "J30 is the outside-world HDMI jack; sheet 11 J300 remains only the internal Intehill HDMI plug." (at 20.32 228.6 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid c11146eb-ee23-4fc9-9dfd-3345b8e5803a))
(text "CEC is ESD-protected but not connected to the Mu or EC in this pass." (at 20.32 236.22 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 2a69a46b-5d20-4733-829f-eb8ce8924ea9))
(text "Pre-layout must verify TCP0 HDMI lane order/polarity against the selected Mu BIOS/reference design." (at 20.32 243.84 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a2b7a130-7a11-4538-a4e7-451e393245ac))
(text "Treat this as HDMI 2.0/18Gbps capable: short routing, low-cap ESD, solid return path, no HDMI 1.4-only parts." (at 20.32 251.46 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 4232786d-4494-4ba6-bcdc-50e43ef2ee35))
(text "TCP1 remains the better future candidate for a Type-C video/PD port if a later BIOS/display plan needs it." (at 20.32 259.08 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid ef8326b8-ed28-4afd-9849-88fe05c3eae6))
